ed="T" n="0717b24"/><persName key="A000871">釋若那跋陀羅</persName>，<name>華</name>言<persName key="A000871">智賢</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000048202">南海波凌</placeName>（亦曰<placeName key="PL000000048202">訶凌</placeName>）國<lb
ed="T" n="0717b25"/>人也，善三藏學。<date notBefore-iso="+0664-02-05" key="j19636161964354" notAfter-iso="+0666-02-12"><name>麟德</name>年中</date>，有<placeName key="PL000000034785">成都</placeName>沙門<persName key="A001438">會<lb
ed="T" n="0717b26"/>寧</persName>欲往<placeName key="PL000000048207">天竺</placeName>，觀<anchor xml:id="beg0717sgsz5"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0717sgsz5"/>聖跡，泛舶西遊，路經<lb
ed="T" n="0717b27"/><placeName key="PL000000048202">波凌</placeName>，遂與<persName key="A000871">智賢</persName>同譯《涅槃》後分二卷<ptr target="#n79"/>。此於<lb
ed="T" n="0717b28"/>《阿笈摩經》<ptr target="#n310"/>內譯出，說<persName key="A002799">世尊</persName>焚棺、收設利羅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g311"/><lb
ed="T" n="0717b29"/>等事，與《大涅槃》頗不相涉。譯畢寄經達<placeName key="PL000000055211">交<pb ed="T" n="0717c" xml:id="T50.2061.0717c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0717c01"/>州</placeName>，<persName key="A001438">寧</persName>方之<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>。至<date notBefore-iso="+0676-12-14" key="j19683121968547" notAfter-iso="+0677-08-06"><name>儀鳳</name>年初</date>，<placeName key="PL000000055211">交州</placeName>都督<persName key="A018714">梁<lb
ed="T" n="0717c02"/>難敵</persName>遣使同<persName key="A001438">會寧</persName>弟子<persName key="A018715">運期</persName>奉表進經，入<lb
ed="T" n="0717c03"/><placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>。<date from-iso="+0678-01-31" key="j19687251969108" to-iso="+0679-02-18">三年戊寅</date>，<placeName key="PL000000042410">大慈恩寺</placeName>沙門<persName key="A008895">靈會</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000042278">東宮</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0717c04"/>啟請施行。<persName key="A018715">運期</persName>奉侍<ref target="#A001438" type="person">其師</ref>，因心<ptr type="glossary" target="#g281"/>莫比，<ref type="person" target="#A001438">師</ref>令<lb
ed="T" n="0717c05"/>齎經行化，故無暇影隨往<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>也。</p> 
